name: 200TH VIDEO: Plane Spotting at Seattle-Tacoma International Airport- "Sea-Tac"
description:
These are the only videos I got from Seattle-Tacoma International Airport (KSEA/SEA) when I was there. I did manage to catch some interesting things, such as the Alaska Dreamliner livery on a 737-800, a Frontier A320 with Sharklets, and a Delta 757-300, as you can see in the video. I know the clips are very shaky, so sorry about that. Anyway, I hope you enjoy my 200th upload!

Thanks for watching, please comment, rate, and subscribe! More videos are coming soon.
_____________________________________________________

Music is "Majestic Hills" by Kevin MacLeod (incompetech.com)
